Tiga-Delapan, Empat-Empat, Lima-Tujuh,

319
00:22:47,958 --> 00:22:49,000
Enam-Nol,

320
00:22:49,500 --> 00:22:51,457
Delapan-Satu,

321
00:22:51,458 --> 00:22:56,958
Sembilan-Enam, Satu-Nol-Sembilan,
Satu-Satu-Satu, majulah.

322
